🚨 Root Cause

Error:

x509: certificate has expired or is not yet valid
current time 2026-04-09 > 2025-06-26

👉 Your Quay registry certificate expired in June 2025


---

✅ Why this happens

Quay was installed ~3 months ago

Self-signed cert was generated with limited validity

Now system date is 2026 → cert expired ❌



---

🧠 Current behavior

Command	Result

normal login	❌ fails
--tls-verify=false	✅ works


👉 So registry is working fine, only TLS validation failing


---

⚡ Quick Workaround (what you did)

